data.description: **PRICE REDUCTION!** Welcome to your dream home in the heart of the Citrus Springs community! This recently newer built (2019) concrete block home is a true gem, boasting not only modern elegance but also the comfort and convenience you need! The beautifully landscaped front yard invites you into a world of charm and sophistication. Once inside, the home unfolds into a large and spacious open concept, accentuated by the split floor plan for added privacy; with luxury vinyl plank "wood look" flooring throughout most of the home, ceramic tile in both bathrooms (as well as granite countertops) and tasteful carpeting in the bedrooms. The living room is a showcase of elegance with tray ceilings accentuated with crown molding, creating a sophisticated ambiance for gatherings and special occasions. The heart of this home is undoubtedly the kitchen; the large breakfast bar/island with granite countertops is not only aesthetically pleasing but also highly functional. The upgraded solid wood cabinetry, featuring soft-close drawers and doors, exudes quality and craftsmanship. All Samsung kitchen appliances are included (refrigerator, stove, microwave range, dishwasher - all warranties are included and will be provided to the new buyer(s)), making this kitchen a haven for both cooking enthusiasts and those who simply appreciate the finer things in life; the washer and dryer are also included with the sale of the home. The generously sized bedrooms ensure everyone in the family has their own space, with the master suite featuring a large bathroom and a large walk-in closet.  Step into the enclosed back porch, an ideal retreat for relaxation but that's not all - the outdoor furniture on the enclosed back porch is a delightful bonus that conveys with the sale. The meticulous attention to detail is evident in the extended and tastefully pavered open back patio, offering the perfect space for entertaining or simply enjoying the serene Florida evenings. Imagine enjoying your morning coffee or hosting intimate gatherings in this charming space. As you explore further, you'll discover the added convenience of a large storage shed outside, perfect for stowing away belongings. The home is already equipped with a front and backyard irrigation system that is also equipped with a rain sensor (located on a white pipe on the side of the home near the a/c unit that will either turn the irrigation system on or keep it off dependent on the rain amount). Worried about HOA fees? Fear not, as this community comes with NO HOA FEES, allowing you the freedom to truly enjoy your home without the extra costs. Also, this home (and its property) is NOT in a flood zone. Tennis enthusiasts will appreciate the local courts less than a mile away, while the community park and playground offer additional recreational options. For nature lovers, the Withlacoochee State Trail is just a short distance from your doorstep (less than a mile away), providing a picturesque setting for walking, hiking, bicycling, and more. Embrace the Florida lifestyle in this meticulously crafted home, where every detail has been carefully considered to offer you the perfect blend of comfort, style, and convenience. Within short driving distance to local shopping, dining and entertainment, this is a one of a kind gem located in a beautiful and peaceful community. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home!
